Skews off the outside half and hangs in the air for enough time for Rashid to get around and take it. Good catch.
comm_cricbuzz: 14.2    Cutting to Uthappa, out Caught by Rashid Khan!! The luck runs out. But it's done the damage. On the shorter side, with the pace taken off the ball as well. Uthappa looks to go ahead with his front-footed pulls but wears it high on the bat with the face swaying upwards as well. For a change, the airy ride finds its destination in the hands of Rashid at mid-wicket. Uthappa c Rashid Khan b Cutting 68(39) [4s-5 6s-4]
